snippet: Dozens of people were injured as protesters clashed with the riot police on Thursday on the second anniversary of a Saudi-led military intervention in Bahrain.
abstract: Dozens of people are injured in Bahrain as protesters clash with riot police on second anniversary of Saudi-led military intervention in country.
